

DIN connector:
    1: PMM signal
    2: +5v
    3: RX
    4: TX





arduino uno:
     0(rx) -> DIN 4(tx)
     1(tx) -> DIN 3(rx)




    10(pb2) -> LCD 4(rs)
     9(pb1) -> LCD 5(rw)
     8(pb0) -> LCD 6(e)
     7(pd7) -> LCD 7(DB0)
     6(pd6) -> LCD 8(DB1)
     5(pd5) -> LCD 9(DB2)
     4(pd4) -> LCD 10(DB3)


    A0(pc0) -> THR
    A1(pc1) -> AIL
    A3(pc2) -> BUTTON
    